        "$:/plugins/twpub/8fa77e24003c4dcc/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/8fa77e24003c4dcc/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-8fa77e24003c4dcc-f09fcd twpub-8fa77e24003c4dcc-6b4cd0\"><p>Project Gutenberg-tm is synonymous with the free distribution of\nelectronic works in formats readable by the widest variety of computers\nincluding obsolete, old, middle-aged and new computers.  It exists\nbecause of the efforts of hundreds of volunteers and donations from\npeople in all walks of life.</p></div>"
