            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/8fa77e24003c4dcc/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-8fa77e24003c4dcc-f09fcd twpub-8fa77e24003c4dcc-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 4.  Information about Donations to the Project Gutenberg\nLiterary Archive Foundation</h4></div>"
