            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/8fa77e24003c4dcc/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-8fa77e24003c4dcc-f09fcd twpub-8fa77e24003c4dcc-6b4cd0\"><p>Please check the Project Gutenberg Web pages for current donation\nmethods and addresses.  Donations are accepted in a number of other\nways including including checks, online payments and credit card\ndonations.  To donate, please visit: https://pglaf.org/donate</p></div>"
