            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-8fa77e24003c4dcc-f09fcd twpub-8fa77e24003c4dcc-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Project Gutenberg-tm eBooks are often created from several printed\neditions, all of which are confirmed as Public Domain in the U.S.\nunless a copyright notice is included.  Thus, we do not necessarily\nkeep eBooks in compliance with any particular paper edition.</p></div>"
